features.description:
Open 8:00 am to dusk, year-round

This restroom is wheelchair accessible.

Men's and women's restrooms are on opposite sides of the wisteria pergola: The men’s restroom is on the north side of the pergola; the women’s restroom is on the south side.

features.title: Arsenal Restrooms
features.description:
Starting January 17, 2023, restrooms on the ground level of the Arsenal will be open to the public only on Saturday, Sunday, and holidays, 9:00 am–5:00 pm.

This restroom is wheelchair accessible.

This restroom does not have an all-gender restroom option.

Restrooms are inside the building, in the basement. Entry is from the south.

This restroom is maintained by NYC Parks.
